OL,3,CEx-constable jailed after misleading
OL,4,Cmurder probe still getting police
OL,5,Cpension
OL,7,FA disgraced former constable now
OL,8,Fbehind bars after misleading the
OL,9,Finvestigation into the murder of
OL,10,FRobert Hamill is still getting a
OL,11,Fpolice pension.
OL,13,FUTV understands Robert Cecil Atkinson
OL,14,Fhas been claiming that pension since
OL,15,Fhe retired from the force.
OL,17,FThis is despite the fact he broke the
OL,18,Flaw decades ago - ringing a suspect
OL,19,Fjust hours after the fatal attack on
OL,20,FRobert Hamill in Portadown in April
OL,21,F1997.
