OL,7,FRetired senior police officer Jon
OL,8,FBurrows says he's shocked by what we
OL,9,Funcovered.
OL,11,F"He has no morals. He puts himself
OL,12,Ffirst. And he has acted in a way
OL,13,Fthat's completely contrary to the
OL,14,Fvalues of policing in Northern
OL,15,FIreland," says Mr Burrows.
OL,17,FLast Friday Atkinson was jailed for a
OL,18,Fyear for conspiring to pervert the
OL,19,Fcourse of justice in connection with
OL,20,Fthe case.
