OL,7,FThe judge telling him he was a
OL,8,Fdisgrace to the uniform.
OL,10,F"It is a disgrace that you as a
OL,11,Fserving police officer should stoop so
OL,12,Flow as to deliberately mislead an
OL,13,Finvestigation...," said Judge Patrick
OL,14,FLynch KC.
