OL,7,F''The public are entitled to expect
OL,8,Fthe highest degree of probity in those
OL,9,Fentrusted to police and enforce the
OL,10,Flaw. You have been a disgrace to your
OL,11,Funiform and have continued to serve as
OL,12,Fa police officer for years afterwards
OL,13,Fas a criminal - there is no other
OL,14,Fdescription for you.''
OL,16,FAtkinson had previously denied telling
OL,17,Fthat murder suspect who was at the
OL,18,Fscene to burn his clothes.
