OL,7,FThe court was told the 71-year-old
OL,8,Fcan't remember what was said in that
OL,9,Fcall to the young man who became a
OL,10,Fmurder suspect.
OL,12,FA charge of murder was later dropped
OL,13,Fdue to insufficient evidence.
OL,15,FUTV can also reveal moves are underway
OL,16,Fto strip Atkinson of his police
OL,17,Fpension. The final decision ultimately
OL,18,Flies with the Justice Minister Naomi
OL,19,FLong.
