OL,7,F''This is an individual with no moral
OL,8,Fcourage, no moral backbone. And it's
OL,9,Freally important now that if public
OL,10,Fmoney can be recovered, and if that
OL,11,Fpension can be forfeited, that the
OL,12,Fauthorities look at those options
OL,13,Fbecause an exemplary example needs to
OL,14,Fbe made of this individual," says Jon
OL,15,FBurrows.
OL,17,FAtkinson was on duty in Portadown that
OL,18,Fnight in April 1997 - one of four
OL,19,Fofficers stationed in a Landrover
OL,20,Fnearby.
